ymptotic expansion,\nwe also show that the correction to the thermal radiation stays of order\n$k_0^{-2}$ or smaller when the spectrum of radiated particle around its peak is\nconcerned.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Apr 1999 10:14:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 28 Sep 1999 15:21:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 29 Sep 1999 06:52:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-10-31"}
